                The President of the Board of Trade (Sir Stafford Cripps)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8191edb9-647d-43e0-8fd2-7027ada4cbd1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
