<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman is perfectly right. I said some thing, but not that.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8191edb9-647d-43e0-8fd2-7027ada4cbd1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1945-06-12/debates/e458a3a5-50b1-4bec-8ad2-daf018a67e95/GovernmentPolicy(MotionOfCensure)#contribution-8191edb9-647d-43e0-8fd2-7027ada4cbd1">
