        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-23d4fa6c-20b8-47c5-b4bb-0bed7254f13c">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-23d4fa6c-20b8-47c5-b4bb-0bed7254f13c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1945-06-12/debates/e458a3a5-50b1-4bec-8ad2-daf018a67e95/GovernmentPolicy(MotionOfCensure)#contribution-23d4fa6c-20b8-47c5-b4bb-0bed7254f13c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">We are glad to hear that quite clearly. We do not drop from 12,000 to 9,000 at the end of the year?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-23d4fa6c-20b8-47c5-b4bb-0bed7254f13c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
